            "text": "Fig. 1: Forest plot demonstrating a meta-analysis comparing mean serum albumin, b leave-one-out meta-analysis comparing mean serum albumin, and c meta-analysis comparing hypoalbuminemia status for patients in severe vs non-severe group (C.I. confidence interval)",
            "type": "figure"
